Habwe, F., Walingo, M. et Abukutsa, M. 2010. Copper and ascorbic acid content of cooked African indigenous vegetables. Poster: International Research on Food Security, Natural Resource Management and Rural Development. Tropentag, Zurich, Suisse. <br/><a href="http://blogs.worldwatch.org/nourishingtheplanet/kenyan-professor-promotes-indigenous-food-to-solve-climate-change-food-crisis" target="_blank">http://www.tropentag.de/2010/proceedings/node63.html</a></p><p>Heever, E. van den et Venter, S.L. 2007. Nutritional and medicinal properties of Cleome gynandra. <i>Acta Horticulturae</i> 752: 127-130.</p><p>
